      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried restarting the router and the thermostat but nothing changed. it still happened again last night. it's so annoying because it feels like there's some tiny little thing just causing chaos in the system for no reason. is there any way to check if it’s a hardware error or if something is actually pulling power from it incorrectly?",
